I understand your use case, but the code you submitted is not done properly and you should do something like the following which is very simple otherwise create a function somewhere on your application to achieve this

``` php
$groupName = 'Administrators';

$group = Sentry::findGroupByName($groupName);

$inGroup = Sentry::inGroup($group);
```

